Comment: 1,0:00:49.45,0:00:49.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.95,0:00:52.07,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,开端便是一切都顺序错乱
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,一成不变的生活地覆天翻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.83,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,很久很久很久以前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.83,0:01:00.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,人还知吃吃喝喝舞中作乐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.71,0:01:03.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,今辛酸痛苦无止境  社会压力超负荷
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.38,0:01:06.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早间新闻将这常态播放着
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.92,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,逼着我睁开双眼  漱口洗脸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.92,0:01:10.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早餐一个汉堡打发  能不能来点奇迹使天地异变
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.68,0:01:12.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做什么梦呢我傻吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.39,0:01:14.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.47,0:01:15.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,I wanna!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.05,0:01:16.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing, dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.39,0:01:17.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Rolling, rolling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.89,0:01:20.14,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Only one, my life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.14,0:01:23.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,不久后人生即将画上句号
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.44,0:01:26.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,仅有空虚又怎够将我填饱？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.65,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.24,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Morning morning
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.24,0:01:34.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,立足原点  保持新鲜
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.62,0:01:37.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做我所愿
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.79,0:01:40.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Every night, every time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.58,0:01:47.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,活至尽兴  玩到疲倦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.67,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
